二級毒品之器具者，處1年以下\r\n有期徒刑、拘役或新臺幣10萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e5%8e%9f%e7%b0%a1%2c33%2c20220826%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,原簡,33,20220826,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"原簡","JNO":"33","JDATE":"20220826","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}